Thomas Hobson (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomas_Hobson_(actor) 0 Thomas "Tommy" Hobson (born June 9, 1984) is an American stage, film, and television actor. He began acting when he was six years old, and received a B.A. in Theatre Studies from Yale University in 2004.
